281
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:58,660
<i>- Detektív Chae Do Jin -</i>

282
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:04,830
<i>(Se Kyung)</i>

283
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:06,700
Se Kyung.

284
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,670
Kde bývaš?

285
00:22:08,970 --> 00:22:13,310
Prečo vyzerajú všetky ulice rovnako?

286
00:22:13,670 --> 00:22:14,670
