00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:28,200
Mal si sa dobre, Yoon Na Moo?

362
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,740
To bolo dobré.

363
00:30:35,110 --> 00:30:37,540
- Hyun Moo.
